                    h3 Theory Application
                    p In this project, I applied animation principles and camera transitions to enhance movement and fluidity.
                    p To create the illusion of weight, I used the “squash and stretch” principle on the bouncing smiley face by adjusting its scale. I also applied the "arcs" principle to ensure a smooth, natural bounce by refining the position keyframes and incorporating ease-ins and ease-outs. Additionally, I fine-tuned the motion by adjusting individual keyframes in the graph editor for a more polished flow.
