                    h2 Challenges and Takeaways
                    p One of the main challenges I faced was determining how to transition smoothly between scenes. For instance, I struggled to find a fitting transition between these two scenes.
                    div.img-wrapper
                        img.half(src="../img/kinetic-challenge1.webp", alt="Typography")
